CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE BODY CHTR.DA_COUNTY
/* Generated on 20-JAN-15 03.39.48.348237000 PM -06:00 */
AS

FUNCTION add (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,county_nm IN VARCHAR2
,county_cd IN VARCHAR2
,territory_id IN NUMBER
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2
) RETURN NUMBER
IS
l_return_pk NUMBER;
BEGIN

chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'begin da_county.add(fx), parms=' || county_nm || '|' || county_cd || '|' || territory_id || '|' || audit_user || '|');
INSERT INTO chtr.t_county a
(
a.county_id
,a.county_nm
,a.county_cd
,a.territory_id
,a.record_stat
,a.created_dttm
,a.created_by
,a.modified_dttm
,a.modified_by
)
VALUES
(
chtr.s_county_id.NEXTVAL
,add.county_nm
,add.county_cd
,add.territory_id
,'A'
,SYSTIMESTAMP
,add.audit_user
,NULL
,NULL
) RETURNING a.county_id INTO l_return_pk;
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_county.add(fx)');
RETURN l_return_pk;

END add;

PROCEDURE add (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,county_nm IN VARCHAR2
,county_cd IN VARCHAR2
,territory_id IN NUMBER
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2
)
IS
BEGIN

chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'begin da_county.add, parms=' || county_nm || '|' || county_cd || '|' || territory_id || '|' || audit_user || '|');
INSERT INTO chtr.t_county a
(
a.county_id
,a.county_nm
,a.county_cd
,a.territory_id
,a.record_stat
,a.created_dttm
,a.created_by
,a.modified_dttm
,a.modified_by
)
VALUES
(
chtr.s_county_id.NEXTVAL
,add.county_nm
,add.county_cd
,add.territory_id
,'A'
,SYSTIMESTAMP
,add.audit_user
,NULL
,NULL
);
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_county.add');

END add;

PROCEDURE add (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,county_id IN NUMBER
,county_nm IN VARCHAR2
,county_cd IN VARCHAR2
,territory_id IN NUMBER
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2
)
IS
BEGIN

chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'begin da_county.add, parms=' || county_id || '|' || county_nm || '|' || county_cd || '|' || territory_id || '|' || audit_user || '|');
INSERT INTO chtr.t_county a
(
a.county_id
,a.county_nm
,a.county_cd
,a.territory_id
,a.record_stat
,a.created_dttm
,a.created_by
,a.modified_dttm
,a.modified_by
)
VALUES
(
add.county_id
,add.county_nm
,add.county_cd
,add.territory_id
,'A'
,SYSTIMESTAMP
,add.audit_user
,NULL
,NULL
);
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_county.add');

END add;

PROCEDURE del (
process_rec IN pkg_logging.t_process_rec
,county_id IN NUMBER
,audit_user IN VARCHAR2
)
IS
BEGIN

chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'begin da_county.del, parms=' || county_id || '|' || audit_user || '|');
UPDATE chtr.t_county a
SET a.record_stat = 'D'
,a.modified_dttm = SYSTIMESTAMP
,a.modified_by = del.audit_user
WHERE a.county_id = del.county_id
;
chtr.pkg_logging.log_debug (process_rec, 'end da_county.del');

END del;

END da_county;
